<i>Well, what do you want me to say?</i>
<i>Accept it.</i>

433
00:28:40,885 --> 00:28:43,179
<i>It's just not something</i>
<i>you're ever going to have.</i>

434
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:46,558
-You don't know that.
