435
00:28:47,267 --> 00:28:48,685
<i>You really want this power thing?</i>

436
00:28:51,438 --> 00:28:53,106
Yes, I do.

437
00:28:54,983 --> 00:28:56,860
<i>Well, if you think it will make you happy…</i>

438
00:28:59,028 --> 00:29:00,613
<i>…then go get it.</i>

439
00:29:01,656 --> 00:29:03,241
<i>I'm sure you'll figure it out.</i>

440
00:29:05,452 --> 00:29:06,578
